languages.text: "Не сомневаюсь". {n}Маражай неслышно пересекает разделяющее вас пространство и наклоняется к вам. Его дыхание щекочет ухо.{/n} "И не заставляй меня ждать".
"I do not doubt it." {n}Marazhai silently closes the distance between you and leans over you, his breath tickling your ear.{/n} "Do not keep me waiting."

languages.text: “我毫不怀疑。”{n}玛拉斋静静地靠了过来，靠在你的耳边。他的呼吸让你的耳朵发痒。{/n}“别让我久等。”

languages.text: 「疑っちゃないさ」{n}マラズハイは静かにあなたとの距離を詰め、顔を寄せてくる。彼の吐息が耳をくすぐった。{/n}「あまり待たせるなよ」
languages.original_text: "I do not doubt it." {n}Marazhai silently closes the distance between you and leans over you, his breath tickling your ear.{/n} "Do not keep me waiting."

languages.text: «No me cabe duda». {n}Marazhai atraviesa la distancia que os separa y se inclina sobre ti. Su aliento te hace cosquillas en la oreja.{/n} «No me hagas esperar».
languages.original_text: "I do not doubt it." {n}Marazhai silently closes the distance between you and leans over you, his breath tickling your ear.{/n} "Do not keep me waiting."

traits.locale_text: «No me cabe duda». {n}Marazhai atraviesa la distancia que os separa y se inclina sobre ti. Su aliento te hace cosquillas en la oreja.{/n} «No me hagas esperar».

languages.text: « Comme de juste. » {n}Marazhai se rapproche silencieusement et se penche vers vous au point que son souffle vous chatouille l'oreille.{/n} « Ne me faites pas attendre. »
languages.original_text: "I do not doubt it." {n}Marazhai silently closes the distance between you and leans over you, his breath tickling your ear.{/n} "Do not keep me waiting."

languages.text: "Daran habe ich keinen Zweifel." {n}Marazhai rückt leise an dich heran und beugt sich über dich, sein Atem kitzelt dabei dein Ohr.{/n} "Lasst mich nicht warten."
languages.original_text: "I do not doubt it." {n}Marazhai silently closes the distance between you and leans over you, his breath tickling your ear.{/n} "Do not keep me waiting."

languages.text: "Buna kuşkum yok." {n}Marazhai, sessizce aranızdaki mesafeyi kapatarak üzerine doğru eğiliyor. Nefesi, kulağına hoş bir melodi gibi geliyor.{/n} "Beni çok bekletme."
